column1: #  The overall V-band flux provided by AAVSO from MJD 58193-58991
#  which has been extinction corrected with E(B-V) = 0.23
#  Thus the luminosities in V-band of the source are estimated L_v = 4*pi*D^2 * flux, for the source distance D = 2.96 kpc
#  The columns are date in modified Julien date, flux and its error
# The uncertainties in the flux are quoted at 1-sigma confidence level
#  The flux and its error are in  units of erg/s/cm^2
